        <heading>2331.  Form of matrimonial agreement</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2331.  Form of matrimonial agreement.
A matrimonial agreement may be executed by the spouses before or during marriage.  It shall be made by authentic act or by an act under private signature duly acknowledged by the spouses.</p>
        </content>
